{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回\"断塔断魂\"，邓定侯在断塔顶上与百里长青对峙。两人曾是互相敬重的朋友，如今却因阴谋而势不两立。百里长青坦言不想亲手杀邓定侯，但两人只能活一个。决斗前，两人互相托付后事——邓定侯托付妻子王盛兰，百里长青则托付一个叫江云馨的女人。激战四十招后，邓定侯落败，关键时刻伪装成胡老五的丁喜出手化解危机。丁喜揭露自己正是百里长青的亲生儿子，其武功与百里长青同源。三人遭到神秘暗器袭击，灯笼熄灭，邓定侯坠塔逃生后与丁喜在塔下汇合。丁喜揭露整件事是青龙会五月十三分舵头领伍先生精心设计的阴谋，故意让所有线索指向百里长青，利用两位英雄互不信任的心理坐收渔利。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我不好，很不好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "你想不到我会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "但是我却早已想到你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我们本来是朋友，是吗？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我们做的事，本来并没有错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "只可惜我们有些地方的做法，并不完全正确，所以才会造成今天这样的结果。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "这实在是很可惜，也很不幸。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "最不幸的，现在我已来了，你也来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "你认为我不该来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我们两个人之中，总有一个是不该来的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "因为我本不想亲手杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "现在我们两个人之中，已势必只有一个能活着回去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "你相信能活着回去的那个人一定是你？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "请！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你的手有伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "无妨。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你所用的武器，就是你的手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "但是我自己也知道，我绝对无法用这只手击败你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "那你用什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "我用的是另一种力量，只有用这种力量，我才能击败你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "这几个月来，你武功好象又有精进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "至少你已真正学会了两招，若想克敌制胜，这两招必不可缺。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "你说的是哪两招？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "忍耐，镇定。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你还有没有什么放不下的事？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "我还有些产业，我的妻子衣食必可无缺，我很放心。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "我若战死，只希望你能替我做一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "放过王盛兰和丁喜，让他们生几个儿子，挑一个最笨的过继给我，也好让我们邓家有个后代。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "为什么要挑最笨的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "傻人多福，我希望他能活得长久些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我若战死，希望你能替我去找一个叫江云馨的女人，把我所有的产业都全交给她。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "因为……因为我知道她有了我的后代。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是胡老五。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我不是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那么你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "丁喜？你就是那个聪明的丁喜？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你刚才用的是什么功夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "功夫就是功夫，功夫只有一种，杀人的是这一种，救人的也是这一种。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你的功夫是谁教你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "没有人教我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "百里长青",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那么你的功夫是从哪里学来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_bai_li_chang_qing",
      "text": "你不知道？真的不知道？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "小丁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你也听见了那暗器的风声？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "是谁在暗算我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "暗器好象是从第五层打上去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我并没有看见任何人从里面出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那么这个人一定还是躲在塔里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "不在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "是你找不到？还是人不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "只要有人在，我就能找到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "无论什么样的暗器，都绝不可能是凭空飞出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "很不可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "有暗器射出，就一定有人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "一定有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "无论什么样的人，都绝不可能凭空无影消失的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那么这个人呢？难道他不是人，是鬼？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "据说这座断塔里本来就有鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你真的相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我不信。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "其实你当然早就知道这个人是谁了，也知道他是怎么来的？怎么走的？却偏偏不肯说出出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你为什么不肯说来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "因为就算说出来，你也不会相信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "因为有很多事都凑巧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "这件事的计划本来很周密，但你们却偏偏总是能凑巧找出很多破绽，每一个破绽，凑巧都可以引出条很有力的线索，所有的线索，又凑巧都只有百里长青一个人能完全符合。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "仔细想一想，这些事的确都太凑巧了些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "但却还不是最凑巧的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "最凑巧的一点是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我凑巧正好是百里长青的儿子。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你的母亲一定就是他刚才要我去找的江夫人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你早已知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "可是你并没有觉得很意外。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我以前的确想到过这一点，但你若没有亲口说出来，我还是不敢确定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你能确定什么？确定百里长青是奸细？是凶手？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我本来的确几乎已确定了，所以…。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "所以你见到他，不问青红皂白就要跟他拼命。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我该问什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你至少应该问问他，他是怎么会到这里来的？在这里等的是谁？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "这约会不是他订的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那么，他等的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "他跟你一样，也是被人骗来的，他等的也正是你要找的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "他等的也是那凶手？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "他看见我来了，难道认为我就是凶手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你看见他在这里，岂非也同样认为他是凶手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "看来伍先生的确是个聪明人，对你们的看法一点也没有错。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "伍先生是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "伍先生就是青龙会五月十三分舵的头领，也就是这整个计划的主持人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "他早已准备了你们一见面就准备出手了，因为你们都是了不起的大英雄，都觉得自己的想法绝不会错，又何必再说废话，先拼个你死我活岂非痛快得多。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 582
    }
  ],
